    <div id="intro">
        <p>
            Para(Special Forces), also known as Para SF, is the special operations unit of the Indian Army. It is
            attached to the Parachute Regiment. The unit specializes in various roles including hostage rescue,
            counter-terrorism, unconventional warfare, special reconnaissance, foreign internal defense,
            counter-proliferation, counter-insurgency, seek and destroy and personnel recovery.
        </p>
        <p>Also known as <b>"Red Devils"</b> </p>
        <p>
        <h4><u> Insignia</u></h4>
        <img src="C:\Users\Harsh kumar balaji\OneDrive\Desktop\project\img_1577765130679_723.jpg" id="p" align="right">
        <ul style="color: rgb(110, 9, 9);">
            <li>Maroon Beret</li>
            <li>Balidan Badge</li>
        </ul><br>
        Formed on 1 July 1966.
        </p>
        <h4 style="display: inline-block;"><u> Motto:-&nbsp; </u></h4>
        <h4 style="display: inline-block; color: rgba(115, 24, 24, 0.715);"> Men Apart every men an emporor , Shatrujeet </h4><br>
        <h4 style="display: inline-block;"><u> War Cry:-&nbsp; </u></h4>
        <h4 style="display: inline-block; color: rgba(128, 0, 0, 0.622);"> Balidan Param Dharam(Sacrifice Before Duty) </h4><br>
        <h4><u>Roles:-</u></h4>
        
        <ul>
