    <div id="operations">
        <h1 style="color: rgb(85, 13, 8);"><u>Operations</u></h1>
    
        <img src="C:\Users\Harsh kumar balaji\OneDrive\Desktop\project\R (1).jpg" id="p" align="right"></div>
        
        <p style="color: cyan;">• Most of the operations of special forces are highly secretive and are never made
            public. <br>
            • But some of the operations are made public and I would be telling some important operations
            among those.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style-type:circle;">
            <li>Operation Mandhol 1971.</li>
            <li>Charcho raid 1971.</li>
            <li>Operation Blue Star 1984.</li>
            <li>Sri Lanka(Operation Pawan) 1987.</li>
            <li>Operation Cactus 1988 , Maldives.</li>
            <li>Kargil War 1999.</li>
            <li>Operation Khukri 2000 , Sierra Leone.</li>
            <li>Operation Apache 2001(company level operation of 9 PARA).</li>
            <li>Operation Summer Storm 2009.</li>
            <li>Counter terrorist operation in Samba.</li>
            <li>Ongoing counter- terrorist and counter-insurgency operations in J&K(Operation Rakshak).</li>
            <li>Myanmar strikes 2015(21 PARA).</li>
           
            <li>Surgical strikes in POK 2016(4&9 PARA).</li>
            
        </ul>
        
        
